	   <tr><td colspan=2>I was looking through allakazam's spell lists for clerics,especially the level 29 spells since I am soon to hit that. I saw this spell 'Sermon of the Righteous'. It puzzled me because it wasn't in any of the other sites I was looking at level 29 spells for, ie eqrealm.com. I was wondering if anyone knew where to get this spell, and if it is vendor sold, which vendor sells it because it looks really kick ass, 240 DoT! And if I remember correctly, only 100 Mana!! That's sick nasty. Anyway, any information is helpful.<br><br>-Sotan<br>26th level Cleric of Prexus<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
