	   <tr><td colspan=2>aye, you are correct, sterris, it is a dot.&nbsp;&nbsp;And yes, it only cost 100 mana.  But it is undead only, last for 1 1/2 min, does 15 damage per tick, and other wise not especally great.  I dont solo often, though if i did i would against undead (for obvious reasons...) so i would use this in that situation.  However, in a group setting, this might not be too teribly effective.  Now, i will admitt that i have never used it, so who knows.  And as for who sells it, the cleric guy in shadowhaven has it.  Also, to see more info on this spell, visit <a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com" target=_new>http://eq.castersrealm.com</a><br><br>Have fun!!<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Mon Feb 18 22:11:19 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
